<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <title>Internship Offer Letter</title>
</head>
<style>
    body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100vh;
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
}

.offer-letter-container {
    text-align: left;
    background-color: #010f8a;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(8, 0, 80, 0.1);
}

h1 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 2em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    
}

p {
    color: #fff;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

strong {
    color: #fff;
}

ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

/* Add additional styles as needed */

</style>
<body>
    <div class="offer-letter-container">
        <h1>Internship Offer Letter</h1>
        <p>Date: <%=certificate_data.date%></p>
        <p>Dear <strong><%=certificate_data.name%></strong></p>
        <p>Congratulations! We are pleased to offer you a position as an intern in <strong><%=certificate_data.internship_name%></strong>. The details of the offer are as follows:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Position:</strong> Intern</li>
            <li><strong>Duration:</strong> 1 Month</li>
            <li><strong>Start Date:</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Location:</strong></li>
            <!-- Add any additional details as needed -->
        </ul>
        <p>We believe that your skills and enthusiasm will make a valuable contribution to our team. Please let us know your acceptance of this offer by <strong></strong>.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or require further information, please feel free to contact us at <strong></strong>.</p>
        <p>We look forward to welcoming you to the team!</p>
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <p><strong></strong></p>
        <!-- Add the company's contact information, signature, or additional details as needed -->
    </div>
</body>
</html>
